<doc>
  <member name="D3D11_VIDEO_COLOR">
    <summary>
      <para>Defines a color value for Microsoft Direct3D 11 video.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>The anonymous union can represent both RGB and YCbCr colors. The interpretation of the union depends on the context.</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/medfound/about-yuv-video">About YUV Video</seealso>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/medfound/direct3d-11-video-structures">Direct3D 11 Video Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D11_VIDEO_COLOR.YCbCr">
    <summary>
      <para>A <see cref="D3D11_VIDEO_COLOR_YCbCrA" /> structure that contains a YCbCr color value.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D11_VIDEO_COLOR.RGBA">
    <summary>
      <para>A <see cref="D3D11_VIDEO_COLOR_RGBA" /> structure that contains an RGB color value.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>